---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTABand from '@/components/CTABand.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Combination Insurance | Heidi Blondin Financial"
  description="Combination insurance provides three-in-one protection of disability, critical illness, and life insurance. Learn more from Heidi Blondin Financial in Kingston, Ontario."
>

  <section class="bg-brand-plum py-20">
    <div class="container-content max-w-3xl">
      <p class="eyebrow-light mb-5">Insurance</p>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-display text-white text-balance" style="font-optical-sizing: auto;">Combination Insurance</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-white section-gap">
    <div class="container-content max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-h2 text-brand-plum mb-6" style="font-optical-sizing: auto;">Combination Insurance</h2>
      <div class="font-sans text-[17px] text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
        <p>What would happen if your paycheque was interrupted for a week, a month or longer?</p>
        <p>Many Canadians don't have the savings to support a short, let alone lengthy, interruption in income. So how will they manage to pay their bills if they get sick or disabled.</p>
        <p>Some insurance carriers are now offering a bundled solution to protect Canadians during their prime working years. This combination insurance provides the three-in-one protection of a disability, critical illness and life insurance policy.</p>
        <p>Combination insurance is more affordable than owning three stand-alone products because of its "pool of money" approach. The amount of insurance put in place is the total amount that can be paid out for any combination of the three potential risks (critical illness, disability and death).</p>
        <p>Combination insurance can provide you with comprehensive protection and peace of mind.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8">
        <a href="#video" class="inline-block font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-brand-plum underline underline-offset-4 hover:text-brand-plum/75 transition-colors">Watch Video</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTABand heading="Contact Heidi for more information on combination insurance and other income-protection strategies." />

</BaseLayout>
